    "## 6. Deterministic stability check\n",
    "\n",
    "Empirically check the bound targeted in the thesis:\n",
    "\n",
    "$$\\|\\Lambda_0(f) - \\Lambda_0(g)\\|_p \\;\\le\\; C_p\\,\\|f - g\\|_\\infty.$$\n",
    "\n",
    "We perturb $\\tau_0$ at the mesh nodes by uniform noise of varying amplitude $\\varepsilon$ and check that the resulting landscape distance is bounded *linearly* by $\\varepsilon$."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 8,
   "id": "ea9517a5",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
