    "## 8. Statistical consistency: $O_P(r_n + h^\\alpha)$\n",
    "\n",
    "Monte-Carlo: for a few sample sizes $n$, repeat\n",
    "\n",
    "* generate fresh data,\n",
    "* fit $\\widehat\\tau_n$ by the R-learner,\n",
    "* compute $\\Lambda_0(f_{n,h})$ on a fixed mesh,\n",
    "\n",
    "and measure the average landscape distance to $\\Lambda_0(\\tau_0)$. This is a numerical illustration of the planned consistency theorem of Section 4.3."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 10,
   "id": "92a1f464",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "name": "stderr",
